  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective study compares the use of indirect pulp therapy and mineral trioxide
      aggregate pulpotomy for pulp therapy of the primary molar with dental caries approaching the
      pulp.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Active, not recruiting</overall_status>
